{"tid":1935331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［TVB日任20/3］勸森美咪做TVB 做臭自己個朵","createTime":"2020-03-20T13:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T04:31:35.000Z","uid":75759,"like":45,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"00344d848ed0da0a45f4941d5bcdaabe15a0ba6c","tid":1935331,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qEJH1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qEJH1R.jpg&h=bfa53c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【偽人狙擊@Mar 20】<br />\n💎中立的森美💎<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/903sammy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F903sammy%2F&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=c723f60f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/903sammy/</a><br />\n1.派嬲/慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.洗版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.互Like留言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.unlike<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n👆🏽到底森美係黃定藍？呢個&quot;薛丁格爾的貓&quot; 嘅問題，你又點睇？留言一齊討論下。不過記得去佢Facebook叫佢離巢，同埋unlike佢。<br />\n<br />\n#Sammy #森美 #SammyLeung<br />\n<br />\n利申：以前返工有聽佢903節目 打發時間幾好<br />\n完全唔明點解佢要接埋啲咩愚弄大家嘅低汁節目做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲們點睇？"},{"pid":"b167270217ccd43d5c1dea95761e6def0fe6479c","tid":1935331,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"886e38c2a3aa0c0bc98adad3221ce375b9e16d96","tid":1935331,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ecd2608d9bed55baa3a896eb44eddf0636d5e65d","tid":1935331,"uid":208412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T13:07:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{